Title: A 1D Model for N-level Atoms Coupled to an EM Field
Authors: Z. S. Bassi and A. LeClair
Comments: 8 pages, Plain TeX
Report-no: CLNS 97/1472
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Optics
Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 40 (1999) 3723-3731
\\
  We construct a model for n-level atoms coupled to quantized electromagnetic
fields in a fibrillar geometry. In the slowly varying envelope and rotating
wave approximations, the equations of motion are shown to satisfy a zero
curvature representation, implying integrability of the quantum system.
